AboutMe: DISCLAIMER: StackExchange sites might occasionally place on users' profiles some logo or slogan publicizing political or ideological positions. Please note that as a user I have no control on what StackExchange places in my profile page, that I do not agree with that practice and that I neither support nor oppose any political or ideological position that StackExchange might choose to express, especially through my profile page. I maintain my membership and participation exclusively because I find StackExchange extremely useful and because I consider almost all of its rules very well thought and effective.
